    <Note Title="Topic" Type="Summary" Ordinal="1" xml:lang="en">Security update for roundcubemail</Note>
    <Note Title="Details" Type="General" Ordinal="2" xml:lang="en">roundcubemail was updated to version 1.0.6 to fix many minor bugs and three security issues.

The following vulnerabilities were fixed:

* CVE-2015-2180: security improvement in DBMail driver of password plugin (shell execution)
* CVE-2015-2181: security improvement in DBMail driver of password plugin (multiple buffer overflows)
* security improvement in contact photo handling</Note>
